NFT's which have already all rates paid (cap=1) or NFT's completely paid due to overcoming total accrued threshold value (cap=2) are also not counted. Cap=3 founders NFT's which are temporarily locked are counted as soon it will be paid again. Additional information which NFT's are already paid will be given on the NFT's list displayed by the front-end. analytics table - displays cummulative percentage of active NFTs on a basis of cap category summary1 table - displays cumulative percentage of active NFTs on a basis of each user NFTs owner.

proposer

period_percentage

threshold
- Upper limit for dividend payment (if roi=1 n/a, if roi=2 cummulative limit, if roi=3 weekly limit).
rates_left
- Number of weekly dividend payment left to pay (only for roi=1).
locked
- Lock of payments (only for roi=3).
